1169			 
1169			toUpper: 
1169			;A is the char. 
1169			;If A is a lowercase letter, this sets it to the matching uppercase 
1169			;18cc or 30cc or 41cc 
1169			;avg: 26.75cc 
1169 fe 61		  cp 'a' 
116b d8			  ret c 
116c fe 7b		  cp 'z'+1 
116e d0			  ret nc 
116f d6 20		  sub 'a'-'A' 
1171 c9			  ret 
